{"tid":134831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"這裡的版主負責人請入","createTime":"2017-02-25T18:51:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-09T11:39:35.000Z","uid":20241,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3bc7b831899ca966671fb59d55be34797151ba91","tid":134831,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T18:51:14.000Z","msg":"請問這裡有無管理員，為什麼這裡有這麼多限制級、成人影片， <br />\n而沒人監管或移到成人版， <br />\n同時充斥大量偏激，種族歧視及反社會的思想<br />\n本來我讓小朋友來貴壇，是嚴禁到成人區， <br />\n以為就此沒問題。 <br />\n怎知道他們來到這裡，看到了那些限制級影片及接觸了那些激進主義思想， <br />\n變得心理開始有問題。 <br />\n請趕快妥善處理，否則，我會向相關部門投訴。"},{"pid":"68474e9ad64d85dfee40e3d7b75a3609111c20fd","tid":134831,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T18:58:38.000Z","msg":"請問這裡有無負責人，為什麼這裡有這麼多限制級、成人影片，卻沒有種子"},{"pid":"d1f35d46ee7fed5097d39159454dd5638be55673","tid":134831,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T17:13:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6670f9efe4f7719ef71b1aa3ecb124cb95aad27c","tid":134831,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T23:39:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請問這裡有無負責人，為什麼這裡有這麼多限制級、成人影片，卻沒有種子</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2d6fe12cee2509400c304ca2cdc7891d3fd8ad3","tid":134831,"uid":47789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T23:45:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57e973f1b0a888a6c4b45b2c6fdf2d6960dc1c64","tid":134831,"uid":9115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T23:54:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>請問這裡有無負責人，為什麼這裡有這麼多限制級、成人影片，卻沒有種子</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/fa